Package src.atm.account

Class AdminAccount

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.atm.account.Account
      • src.atm.account.AdminAccount

  • public final class AdminAccount
extends Account
    This class provides special functionality and privileges that allow direct access and control of other bank accounts. An admin account can change values stored in the accounts and view account information.

    This class cannot be inherited. This class inherits Account.
    Version:
    01/21/2018
    Author:
    Joshua Ciffer
